      <h3>Starting a Work Session</h3>
      <div class="help-step">
        <div class="help-step-num">1</div>
        <div class="help-step-content">
          <strong>Open the task</strong>
          <p>Click on the task from your task list to open the detail page.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="help-step">
        <div class="help-step-num">2</div>
        <div class="help-step-content">
          <strong>Click "Start Session"</strong>
