        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="help-step">
        <div class="help-step-num">3</div>
        <div class="help-step-content">
          <strong>Work on the task</strong>
          <p>You can leave the page and come back. Your session stays active until you complete or end it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Undoing a Completion</h3>
      <p>If you completed a task by mistake, you can undo the completion for today. On the task detail page, click <strong>"Undo Completion"</strong>. This resets today's completion record and removes the associated reward entry if one was created.</p>

      <div class="help-warn">
        <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle"></i>
        <div>Undoing a completion also removes the reward entry for that day. Make sure you truly need to undo before confirming.</div>
      </div>

      <h3>Logging a Past Completion</h3>
      <p>If you forgot to mark a recurring task as complete on a previous day, you can backfill it:</p>
      <div class="help-step">
        <div class="help-step-num">1</div>
        <div class="help-step-content">
          <strong>Open the recurring task</strong>
          <p>Navigate to the task detail page.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="help-step">
        <div class="help-step-num">2</div>
        <div class="help-step-content">
