      <h2><i class="bi bi-pencil-square"></i> Attendance Override</h2>
      <p class="topic-desc">Override a user's attendance record for a specific day. This allows admins to correct attendance when the automatic tracking does not reflect reality.</p>
      <span class="help-role-badge admin">LOCAL_ADMIN</span>

      <h3>Override Options</h3>
      <p>You can change a user's attendance status for any day to one of the following:</p>
